//! Core biomeOS integration tests
//! 
//! This test suite validates core biomeOS functionality with focus on
//! primal coordination, biome lifecycle management, and eco-system harmony.

// NOTE: These integration tests are currently disabled as they test against
// an API that hasn't been implemented yet. The actual biomeOS core implements
// a different API structure. These tests serve as documentation for the
// intended future API.

